Toya'caen canqque tsaiqui'ye jacan'fasi cca'indeccu tise'pama ñotsse in'jamba chigambian'faye in'jan'fa. Nane ñotsse in'jamba tise'pama “injama'pa atesian'su” qquen chigambiañe tsu in'jan'fa.
